Package io.opencaesar.oml

Interface Argument

All Superinterfaces:
Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArgumentImpl
public interface Argument extends Element
A representation of the model object 'Argument'. Argument is an element that represents a variable name, a [=Literal=], or an [=NamedInstance=] specified in a [=predicate=].

The following features are supported:

  • Variable
  • Literal
  • Instance
